dialog.body: Hello, thank you for contacting SafeDrives Auto Insurance. My name is John Griffin. May I have your name, please?
Hello, my name is Christina Powell.
Nice to meet you, Christina. Could you please provide me with your policy number for verification purposes?
Of course, my policy number is eight five three two one.
Thank you, Christina. Additionally, could you confirm the make and model of your insured vehicle?
Yes, it's a two zero one eight Toyota Camry.
Great, thank you for the information. Is there any specific reason for your call today, Christina?
I need to add a new driver to my policy.
Understood. Thank you for letting us know, Christina. We will take care of that for you. Is there anything else I can assist you with today?
No, that will be all. Thank you, John.
You're welcome, Christina. Thank you for choosing SafeDrives Auto Insurance. Have a great day!
